## SMALL IS BEAUTIFUL

Before creating any file: list target folder, search repo for similar
names, check related folders/imports, and prefer editing existing
files. Ask for explicit confirmation when in doubt.

## HYGIENE

After edits: run build/lint/tests where applicable. Your ultimate goal
is a green CI and to have all bugs outlined by the human fixed.

